reviews.review_text: Top Nothch Just when i thought this awesome show could not sound any better, along comes this CM FLAC24 and itis a testimony of superb recording coupled with a night the band were firing on all cylinders. A pure joy listening with the headphones, even the tuning is satisfying. Thanks to all who made it possible.
